<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pesanan Masuk - Arum Dalu</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1f2d3d 0%, #172330 100%);
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .card {
            width: min(420px, 100%);
            background: #2a3b4c;
            border: 1px solid #34495e;
            border-radius: 28px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(39, 174, 96, 0.14);
            color: #27ae60;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }
        .muted {
            color: #95a5a6;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f39c12, #f1c40f);
            color: #162534;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="badge">Pesanan Berhasil Dikirim</div>
        <h1>Order Anda Sudah Masuk</h1>
        <p class="muted">Kasir dan dapur sudah menerima order Anda. Jika perlu bantuan, gunakan tombol layanan dari halaman menu digital.</p>
        <% if (orderId) { %>
            <p class="muted">ID order: <strong><%= orderId %></strong></p>
        <% } %>
        <a class="btn" href="javascript:history.back()">Kembali ke Menu</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
